<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <div class="about-left">
      <div class="avatar">🌿</div>
      <h2 class="about-name">小周</h2>
      <p class="about-title">INFP · 雨林脑程序员</p>
      <div class="about-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/mirukuz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub ↗</a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/mirukuz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Twitter ↗</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-right">
      <p>我是小周，一个 INFP 独立开发者。习惯 vibe coding——跟着感觉走，一个人当一家公司，从产品到设计到代码全包了。</p>
      <p>我做的产品围绕两个主题：个人成长，以及人与人之间的真实连结。不追流量，只想做对某些人真正有用的东西。</p>
      <p>「雨林脑」（Rainforest Mind）是心理学家 Paula Prober 提出的概念，用来描述那些思维密集、感受深刻、好奇心旺盛的人——就像热带雨林一样，层次丰富，充满生命力。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: #f0ede8;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .about-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .avatar {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5c6b4a, #8fa876);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-name {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #2d3a1e;
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #8fa876;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .about-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .about-links a {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #5c6b4a;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .about-links a:hover {
    color: #2d3a1e;
  }

  .about-right p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #3a4a2a;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .about-right p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
